data.description:
Almost a whole acre in Windmill Farms and Deer Creek Schools! Beautiful Spruce floor plan! This home is 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, 3 car  garage, formal dining and separate breakfast area. Upon entering the home you walk through the foyer into the living room and huge open kitchen. The master suite features separate double vanities, jetted tub and custom tile walk in shower and huge walk in closet. Home has just started construction so selections can still be made! Don't miss the opportunity to customize this gorgeous home!

For more information on this home text AVAILABLE to 59559
